title: No, Fairfax County Didn’t Give Biden 100K Extra Votes in Virginia
subtitle: A quickly corrected clerical error was exploited to further yet another false claim about voter fraud after the 2020 election.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: Fairfax County, Virginia, "gave" U.S. 2020 Democratic presidential candidate Joe Biden an extra 100,000 votes.
